              <p>We propose to present in this demo a large set of web audio plugins (aka web audio modules), real-time effects (most classic audio effects, tube guitar amplifier simulations, etc.), instruments (synthesizers, samplers,) along with an open source DAW (wamstudio) and a real time collaborative host called sequencer.party. Web Audio Modules (WAM) is a standard for developing Web Audio plugins and hosts first proposed in 2015, that recently had a major update in 2021 for its 2.0 version.</p>
